reviewText: Easier to buy these then collect off cable. Getting them in order helps the series make more sense. Looking forward to getting the rest.

I'm looking forward for this to be released. I have almost all of the Pokemon DVD's except for the Johto. I have a few DVD's from the Johto but, not all of them.

I have a prediction of episodes for this DVD.

1. Uncrushing Defeat
2. Promating Healthy Tangrowth

5. Three sides to Every Story
6. Strategy Begins at home
7. A Faux Oak Finish!
8. Historial Mystery Tour

All the Pokemon series and movies are very entertaining and funny with its witty humor!  I still watch them with my now ADULT son!

Im still a fan of Pokemon collect the anime series so these box set were a must . I do love the Diamond and Pear series im a fan of Dawn , great show and im still into Pokemon . I collect the series , movies and figures , don't play the games .
My granddaughter loved it since she is a real Pokemon fan.  It made a great gift and all the grandkids enjoyed watching!
